# Mher Thar Ser — Design System & Coding Standards

Restaurant discovery & booking platform · Bangkok · Bilingual EN + မြန်မာ

---

## Brand

- **Red**: `--brand #E0052D` · hover `--brand-hover #C00528` · light `--brand-light #FF1A45`
- **Gold**: `--gold #D4A853` — ratings, price tiers only
- Brand dim/border companions: `--brand-dim`, `--brand-border` for ghost surfaces
- Semantic: `--success #3DAA6E` · `--warning #E09B2D` · `--danger #E84040` · `--info #4A9FD4`
  - Each has `-dim` (alpha bg) and `-border` (alpha border) variants

---

## Theming

Theme toggled via `data-theme="light|dark"` on `<html>`. Never hardcode hex values that map to a token.

```css
/* ✅ always use tokens */
color: var(--text-primary);
background: var(--card);

/* ❌ never hardcode */
color: #0a0a08;
background: #242424;
```

**Light — Arctic Ice**
- `--bg #F5FBFF` · `--surface #FFF` · `--card #EEF8FF` · `--card-hover #E4F4FF`
- `--text-primary #0A0A08` · `--text-secondary #3A3933` · `--text-muted #5C5B54`
- `--border rgba(0,0,0,0.08)` · `--border-strong rgba(0,0,0,0.14)`

**Dark — Ferie Black**
- `--bg #1A1A1A` · `--surface #222` · `--card #242424` · `--card-hover #2A2A2A`
- `--text-primary #F5F4EF` · `--text-secondary #A09F97` · `--text-muted #5C5B54`
- `--border rgba(255,255,255,0.07)` · `--border-strong rgba(255,255,255,0.12)`

Glassmorphism pattern (nav, sheets):
```css
background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 85%, transparent);
backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
```

---

## Typography

| Font | Variable | Weights | Use |
|------|----------|---------|-----|
| **Pogonia** | `--font-sans` | 100–900 (9 weights) | All Latin text (primary font) |
| Noto Sans Myanmar | `--font-my` | 400–700 | All Burmese text |

Body default: `15px / 1.6`. Burmese text always gets `line-height: 1.9; letter-spacing: 0.01em` via the `.my` class.

**Type scale**
| Role | Size | Weight | Tracking |
|------|------|--------|----------|
| Hero H1 | `clamp(42px,7vw,72px)` | 900 | `-2px` |
| Hero H2 | `clamp(32px,5.5vw,48px)` | 700 | `-1px` |
| Card title | `15px` | 600–700 | `-0.2px` |
| Body | `15px` | 400 | `0` |
| Caption / meta | `12–13px` | 400–600 | `0` |
| Badge / label | `11px` | 600–700 | `+0.02em` |
| Burmese body | `15px` | 400 | `+0.01em` |

---

## Spacing

Base unit **4px**. Use multiples: `4 8 12 16 20 24 32 40 48 64 80`.

| Context | Value |
|---------|-------|
| Inline gap (icon + label) | 6–8px |
| Component inner padding | 16px |
| Card padding | 20px (`px-5 py-5`) |
| Section gap | 24–32px |
| Page horizontal (mobile) | 16px |
| Page horizontal (desktop) | 24–32px |
| Mobile top bar height | 56px |
| Desktop nav height | 64px |

---

## Border Radius

```
--radius-sm   6px    tags, small chips, icon buttons
--radius-md   10px   inputs, buttons, small cards
--radius-lg   16px   cards, panels, modals
--radius-xl   20px   large surfaces
--radius-2xl  28px   bottom sheets, hero blocks
--radius-full 9999px pills, avatars, badge chips
```

---

## Shadows & Motion

**Shadows:** `--shadow-sm` (micro) → `--shadow-md` (cards) → `--shadow-lg` (hover) → `--shadow-xl` (modals) → `--shadow-brand` (CTA hover)

**Motion tokens:**
```
--dur-fast   150ms   colour, opacity
--dur-base   220ms   card lift, border
--dur-slow   350ms   page-level enter
--ease-out   cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94)
--ease-spring cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1)
```

**Animation utilities:** `.animate-fade-in` · `.animate-slide-up` · `.animate-slide-down` · `.animate-overlay` · `.animate-spin`

**Z-index layers:**
```
--z-base 0 · --z-raised 10 · --z-overlay 100 · --z-modal 200 · --z-toast 300 · --z-nav 400
```

