## Logo

| Asset | File | Use |
|-------|------|-----|
| **Vertical wordmark** | `logo_mascot_text_vertical.png` | Desktop/laptop nav + footer, paired with horizontal (`LOGO_VERTICAL_SRC` / `LOGO_SRC`) |
| **Horizontal wordmark** | `logo_mascot_text_horizontal.png` | Same pairing on desktop/laptop; mobile top bar alone (`LOGO_HORIZONTAL_SRC`) |
| Circle | `logo_mascot_circle.png` | Optional icon-only (`LOGO_CIRCLE_SRC`) |

**Never** place the PNG inside a container with a background colour, border ring, or `overflow: hidden`.

